Oxfam America Website Content

Report last updated on May 31, 2019 at 01:00 PM

Oxfam Website Content Summary

Period between 2019-05-29 and 2019-05-30.

Quality Page Views are defined as follows:
Immersive Stories:
User spends 45 or more seconds on a page and scrolls to at least 50% of the page.
User spends 45 or more seconds on a page and views at least 50% of any audio or video elements on the page.
User clicks CTA.

Non Immersive Stories:
User spends 30 or more seconds on a page and scrolls to at least 50% of the page.
User spends 30 or more seconds on a page and views at least 50% of any audio or video elements on the page.
User clicks CTA

Dataset Summary Statistics

This is a summary of the content level data in this report.
For example, the average number of unique page views for a given piece of content in this dataset was: 5.
The 3rd Quartile (3rd Qu.) for unique page views of content in this dataset was 3. This means that 75% of the content in this data set had less than or equal to 3 unique page views.
The most number of unique page views any given content had was 204. The least number of unique page views any given content had was 1.
